{"tid":183371,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"地產Smart Lady：阿Pan為上車誓不碌卡！","createTime":"2017-04-02T05:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T15:19:40.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4acb3985daf3cf900379f110ade25b92f18c37","tid":183371,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_01b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=e2153215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港地置業難，有港女講明要有層2,000呎樓的男人才會考慮。不過今期「地產Smart Lady」主角、90後的Pan雖然是「Sell樓為業」，但卻不認同這種價值觀，直指「擇偶」並非「擇樓」；不介意與未來另一半一起努力賺錢組織家庭。她的「貼地」目標，是4年後買個逾500萬港元的元朗舊樓2房單位；「秘密武器」是「一張卡都冇」。<br />\n<br />\nPan長相甜美，氣質有點像韓星允兒，現職美聯元朗大馬路分行高級物業顧問。原來半年前Pan才由Part-time轉做Full-time入行，「自己性格好動，鍾意四圍走，呢行可以接觸到人，睇樓亦冇咁悶，朋友介紹下先做Part-time，睇吓自己適唔適合呢行」。<br />\n<br />\nPan直言做地產代理非想像中容易，「開頭真係一張白紙，主要周六、日喺新盤撈客，時間長企得耐，夏天30幾度最難捱，仲要不時畀人不禮貌對待，唔係咁好受。」幸好Pan有好上司及同事無私教導，「有次新盤撈客做到好夜，仲要返分行收舖，真係好攰好想放棄，上司見到就同我傾，畀我睇佢記錄咗佢入行20幾年來工作安排嘅厚厚記事簿，發覺原來成功唔係僥倖，時刻喺度做準備，所以更加堅定自己繼續努力工作。」<br />\n<br />\nPan的辛勤及堅持終有回報，「有次心態夠強，跟同事在新盤現樓企足13個鐘到凌晨2點，真係撞到有客人揸車來睇環境，最終成功協助佢買樓。」促成買賣加上客戶變成朋友帶來的滿足感，增加Pan入行的決心。<br />\n<br />\n她坦言，做地產代理多勞多得，辛苦賺取收入是想提升生活質素。未置業的她不介意與男友夾份儲首期，Dream Home係180度海景大單位。她深明置業難，不能一步登天，首個目標是4年後可在元朗買個逾500萬元的舊樓2房單位，首期逾100萬元，先放租幾年補貼供樓支出才自住。<br />\n<br />\n「唔係話住1房單位屈就，始終組織家庭2間房好啲，希望盡自己最大努力達成目標，即使住舊樓都唔緊要。」<br />\n<br />\n對於有港女揀男友條件是至少有層2,000呎樓，Pan並不認同，「鍾意一個人唔會用層樓來作為考慮條件，覺得有啲荒謬。」她不介意與男友一起努力賺錢置業，「今時今日儲首期難，如果有『父幹』、『慈母』當然係開心事，但大前題係先靠自己，唔夠先搵家人協助比較好。」<br />\n<br />\n問到如何儲首期，Pan強調自己都係一般年輕人，不會不享樂，惟她會努力賺錢，將收入一半儲起，而且應使則使。為儲首期早日達成夢想，Pan「鐵定」不使未來錢，「從小屋企養成唔使未來錢嘅習慣，自己從來冇申請過一張信用卡，冇卡用咪唔會唔覺意使大咗」。<br />\n<br />\n一張信用卡都冇；相比時下愛碌卡消費的年輕人，絕對是稀有品種。Pan為置業可以去到咁盡，時下愛碌卡消費的年輕人，做得到嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_02b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_02b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=ba0b9b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPan上車目標為500萬左右的元朗2房單位。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_03b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_03b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=3b2efe1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_04b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_04b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=0a36c96d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_05b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_05b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=8b13ac4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_06b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_06b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=d30d0562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_07b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_07b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=52286045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_08b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_08b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=b13d6b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/photo/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_09b.jpg?20170330132019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001_09b.jpg%3F20170330132019&h=30180eab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPan半年前才轉做Full-time代理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170330%2Fbkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001.html&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=22f984c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170330/bkn-20170330112429683-0330_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5f551821f11e045199688aa779465e2b484ad187","tid":183371,"uid":704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:11:37.000Z","msg":"有冇特別服務先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2bac5e733af849efe1dbf6743e1a71d39bd7bb","tid":183371,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"有無學下belle師姐呀 ?"},{"pid":"5a7926fb7a6e8f2c0146e0a2ac8d4ef88e49fc6f","tid":183371,"uid":33505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"點解遠照同近照差咁遠咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺咪我眼矇"},{"pid":"ecef49866f13dcf71cca51a73438d7e56f8bae75","tid":183371,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解遠照同近照差咁遠咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h